item.title: How Great Thou Art / O Lord my God
item.description: Oh Lord My God, When I In Awesome Wonder, Consider All The Worlds Thy Hands Have Made; I See The Stars, I Hear The Rolling Thunder, Thy Power Throughout The Universe Displayed. Then Sings My Soul, My Saviour God, To Thee, How Great Thou Art! How Great Thou Art! Then Sings My Soul, My Saviour God, To Thee, How Great Thou Art! How Great Thou Art! And When I Think, That God, His Son Not Sparing;
